data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Step inside and be greeted by an expansive open floor plan on the main level. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a culinary enthusiast's paradise. With modern stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and more. Venture upstairs and discover the spacious loft area. The master bedroom is a true retreat, with abundant space to unwind. A highlight of the master suite is the expansive walk-in closet and ensuite. Outside, the decently sized backyard provides a canvas for your outdoor dreams. From gardening to entertaining, this space invites you to enjoy the outdoors in your own private sanctuary. Conveniently located in Timbercreek, you'll have easy access to to I95. Whether it's shopping, dining, parks, or schools, everything you need is within reach. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the blend of comfort, style, and functionality that defines this remarkable property.
